# Astro Framework Development Rules

## Core Tech Stack
1. **Framework**: Astro 5.8+ (Static Site Generator)
2. **Package Manager**: pnpm
3. **UI Framework**: Tailwind CSS 4.1+ + DaisyUI 5.0+
4. **Icons**: Lucide (via @iconify-json/lucide)
5. **Components**: React 19+ (for interactive components)
6. **TypeScript**: Strict mode configuration

## Project Structure Standards
```
src/
├── assets/          # Static assets (images, fonts, etc.)
├── components/      # Reusable components
│   ├── mdx/        # MDX-specific components
│   └── widgets/    # Page-level components
├── content/        # Content collections (blog posts, data, etc.)
├── interface/      # TypeScript interface definitions
├── layouts/        # Page layout templates
├── pages/          # Route pages
├── styles/         # Global styles
└── utils/          # Utility functions
```